{"tid":550660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國調查：中國品牌最值得信賴　超德美日得第一","createTime":"2018-02-05T03:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T07:00:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f8cce1338082a1ef04738d8a2da1634925e58a","tid":550660,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:14:23.000Z","msg":"日前企鵝智酷聯合騰訊指數，公佈一份《品牌影響力指數》報告，內文中提道，中國消費者認為，中國品牌的可信賴度在心目中高居第一，超越美國、德國、日本等國。<br />\n《品牌影響力指數》報告中指出，中國品牌的可信賴度，在「各國品牌信賴度」、「各國品牌獨特性」、「不考慮價格和購買便利性，最想購買國家的品牌」、「目前購買哪個國家的品牌比較多」的排名中，中國分別以3.94分、3.85分、51.8%、86.1%，超越英國、美國、德國、日本等國，全部項目都奪得第一名。<br />\n報告分析，消費者對國產品牌保持認可和積極的態度，59%的消費者會越來越多地購買中國品牌，僅有9%的消費者會買的越來越少。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180204/640_55805417cfb157f095b7e4a432d8d3db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180204%2F640_55805417cfb157f095b7e4a432d8d3db.jpg&h=c9945e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180204/640_b31d82056d8f590b711ef0c0d0dbc433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180204%2F640_b31d82056d8f590b711ef0c0d0dbc433.jpg&h=f3d3d1cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180204/640_7a071f48f5a54e156ac0b00f36c2903a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180204%2F640_7a071f48f5a54e156ac0b00f36c2903a.jpg&h=95be7a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180204/1292024/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180204%2F1292024%2F&d=wki6ITxkegJeqrB7EpOSB7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4374fa17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180204%2F1292024%2F&h=be9d1e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180204/1292024/</a>"},{"pid":"03f9116b2dd1f01a8fd3adc34394a6a2a597dc74","tid":550660,"uid":35706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"ffaa48e2dbc64bd2ee395a59268625b8a63a0bb3","tid":550660,"uid":2772,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:15:35.000Z","msg":"好可惜<br />\n中國調查最不值得信賴"},{"pid":"20eb82a60068bce878eb91c063fa0d7e05a3dde7","tid":550660,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4de2d22e14899734645264d354666e7a92def30","tid":550660,"uid":34336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:16:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1aa37d2027c8cfeb6dab5876e1c8557166f5cd8","tid":550660,"uid":37442,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:18:55.000Z","msg":"買返自己既奶粉先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dd60f29c37e9b2753d6a00ae4892af54c02522","tid":550660,"uid":38671,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:18:59.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n都唔知點解咁多水貨狗"},{"pid":"a087a7f6d25e78515c5848d17674f98905c59dad","tid":550660,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"感謝提供本日最佳笑話"},{"pid":"5a0b6806d5976805c9fc636059ff0c1d7811128d","tid":550660,"uid":73849,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"喺爆炸呢方面嚟講，中國品牌真係最值得信賴嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae6955db147c167e9a7f10329eb8a2f4be81039","tid":550660,"uid":2772,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"相信呢份係記名調查"},{"pid":"0ef6440f1a05b71c8b38762e391d8c90f7f586f0","tid":550660,"uid":63909,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"中國調查：中國品